Post-Match Reflections: Pakistan captain Babar Azam: 'We needed this win.'
Canada captain Saad Bin Zafar: 'It was disappointing.'
Miscellaneous Highlights: This was the highest successful chase at this New York ground
Others: Pakistan have chalked up their first win to just about keep their qualifying flame alive.
Canada slip below their opponents to fourth - like Pakistan they have two points, but now have a negative run-rate so their chances of qualification are even slimmer.
